o-width-down/536?cb=20230509221334 2x\" class=\"pi-image-thumbnail\" data-relevant=\"1\" alt=\"Blake Croyle Infobox CP2077\" width=\"270\" height=\"360\" data-image-key=\"Blake_Croyle_Infobox_CP2077.png\" data-image-name=\"Blake Croyle Infobox CP2077.png\" />\n\t\t\n\t</a>\n\t\n</figure>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Biographical Information</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"status\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Status</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">Dependent</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"dod\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Date of Death</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">2077 (dependent)</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"place_of_death\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Place of Death</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Kabuki\" title=\"Kabuki\">Kabuki</a> (dependent)</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"home\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Home</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Night_City\" title=\"Night City\">Night City</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Physical Information</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"gender\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Gender</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">Male</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"hair_color\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Hair Color</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">Black</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"equipment\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Equipment</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Defender\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Defender\">Defender</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Faction Information</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"affiliation\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Affiliation</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Animals\" title=\"Animals\">Animals</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color pi-collapse pi-collapse-closed\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Appearances</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"appears_games\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Game(s)</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><i><a href=\"/wiki/Cyberpunk_2077\" title=\"Cyberpunk 2077\">Cyberpunk 2077</a></i></div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n</aside>\n\n<b>Blake Croyle</b> is a character in <i><a href=\"/wiki/Cyberpunk_2077\" title=\"Cyberpunk 2077\">Cyberpunk 2077</a></i>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Biography\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Biography</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Associated_Quests\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Associated Quests</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Shards\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Shards</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Biography\">Biography</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fcyberpunk.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FBlake_Croyle%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Blake Croyle likes to give the impression of a polite, well-spoken man whose job is simply to collect the debts of those he so graciously lent some <a href=\"/wiki/Eurodollar\" title=\"Eurodollar\">eurodollars</a> to out of the kindness of his own heart. The truth of the matter, however, is that he is a predator, barely a step above the brutish thugs from the <a href=\"/wiki/Animals\" title=\"Animals\">Animals</a> that he himself pays to do his dirty work. And choom, he puts the \"shark\" in loanshark.\n</p><p>See, he uses a very simple system: first and foremost, don't let your mark realize what a gonk they are right away. Be their friend, offer your generosity...and then, when the time comes, snap the trap shut around their wallet just as they start to see your true colors. And if they don't pay? Well, no big deal--just give them a good scare, smash their things up a little, give them a few bruises or perhaps a harsh shove and a mild concussion to show you mean business, and throw in some threats to their family if they need some extra \"encouragment.\" And, when they open that fat wallet of theirs to pay out the eddies owed, you know they're yours. This process has worked for Croyle countless times before, and with it, he rakes in a fat stack of eddies from across the city.\n</p><p>Nowadays, Mr. Croyle has recently set his ambitious sights on the store chain of one <a href=\"/wiki/Roger_Wang\" title=\"Roger Wang\">Roger Wang</a>. Even though he never actually <i>lent</i> Wang any money, Blake believes he is owed simply for the privilege of giving Roger \"business advice\" regarding his money troubles. So, he takes a payout from Wang--along with one of Wang's shops in <a href=\"/wiki/Kabuki\" title=\"Kabuki\">Kabuki</a>, as \"interest.\" And he has no intention of stopping there.\n</p><p>Unfortunately, it is here that Blake made an error: unlike his other clients who could be cowed and shaken down, Roger took his concerns to one <a href=\"/wiki/Regina_Jones\" title=\"Regina Jones\">Regina Jones</a>, a local fixer who just so happens to have no love for Mr. Croyle, or his predatory actions against the people in her neighborhood. Soon enough, Regina gets a hold of <a href=\"/wiki/V_(character)\" title=\"V (character)\">V</a> and explains Roger's plight to them, before instructing the Solo to put an end to Blake Croyle's business dealings--permanently.\n</p><p>Should V take the job, they find Blake set up in Roger's former shop, reclining and running his business out of a room in the back while occasionally chatting on the holo or to his Animals bodyguards, which V must either sneak or fight past to reach him. From here, V may offer some \"business advice\" of their own--the unspoken kind, which may be immediately lethal, ending the life of Mr. Croyle right there, or perhaps nonlethal, allowing the loanshark to be gathered up and stuffed into the trunk of a waiting Archer, for express delivery to the fixer to be dealt with as she sees fit.\n</p><p>And so, the career, and life, of Blake Croyle draws to a close, bringing with it a very valuable lesson: Some debts are paid with blood rather than eddies.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Associated_Quests\">Associated Quests</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fcyberpunk.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FBlake_Croyle%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Gig:_Shark_in_the_Water\" title=\"Gig: Shark in the Water\">Shark in the Water</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Shards\">Shards</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fcyberpunk.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FBlake_Croyle%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Archived_Conversation:_Ben_Azaria_and_Sasquatch\" title=\"Archived Conversation: Ben Azaria and Sasquatch\">Archived Conversation: Ben Azaria and Sasquatch</a></li><li><a href=\"/wiki/Archived_Conversation:_Blake_Croyle_and_Tim_Autry\" title=\"Archived Conversation: Blake Croyle and Tim Autry\">Archived Conversation: Blake Croyle and Tim Autry</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fcyberpunk.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FBlake_Croyle%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/My_beloved_debtors\" title=\"My beloved debtors\">My beloved debtors</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Debt\" title=\"Debt\">debt</a></li></ul>\n</div>"}, "images": ["Blake_Croyle_Infobox_CP2077.png", "2077Icon.png"]}}